highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 276 weeks straight.
Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Moscow Mule” is the highest at #2.
“Until I Found You” by Stephen Sanchez is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 98 spots at #83.
“N95” by Kendrick Lamar is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #3.
